### Create a new pet
POST http://localhost:5000/api/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buddy",
  "age": 3,
  "breedId": 1,
  "shelterId": 1
}

### Get all pets
GET http://localhost:5000/api/pets

### Get a specific pet by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/pets/1

### Update a pet
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/pets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Buddy",
  "age": 4,
  "breedId": 1,
  "shelterId": 1
}

### Delete a pet
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/pets/1